dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Adams County, WI  2018
dc_description_s: These data layers represent roads and right of way for Adams County, Wisconsin in 2018. They are feature classes within the geodatabase Adams_Roads_ROW_2018.gdb. The features inlcuded in this geodatabase are ADAMS_ROADS_2018 and ADAMS-ROW_2018.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: www.adamscountylandrecords.com
